| 9  | 210   | 210    | Square |
+----+-------+--------+--------+
| 44 | 200   | 200    | Square |
+----+-------+--------+--------+
| 11 | 172   | 172    | Square |
+----+-------+--------+--------+
| 7  | 150   | 150    | Square |
+----+-------+--------+--------+
| 50 | 140   | 140    | Square |
+----+-------+--------+--------+
| 12 | 138   | 138    | Square |
