| 21 | 120   | 120    | Square |
+----+-------+--------+--------+
| 3  | 100   | 100    | Square |
+----+-------+--------+--------+
| 42 | 50    | 50     | Square |
+----+-------+--------+--------+
| 22 | 25    | 25     | Square |
+----+-------+--------+--------+
| 26 | 800   | 600    | 4:3    |
+----+-------+--------+--------+
| 36 | 400   | 300    | 4:3    |
